1
00:05:59,916 --> 00:06:00,749
Are you good?

2
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,750
Everything is good.

3
00:06:02,041 --> 00:06:02,875
Who is this?

4
00:06:04,791 --> 00:06:05,958
Wasn't Leo your cousin?

5
00:06:37,083 --> 00:06:38,250
Put them in the case.

6
00:06:39,208 --> 00:06:41,708
Come round the back,
I want to have a word.

7
00:08:23,041 --> 00:08:24,500
Today is different.

8
00:08:25,625 --> 00:08:27,625
This isn't your usual run.

9
00:08:29,208 --> 00:08:31,833
You're going to transport
two sets of diamonds.

10
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:35,166
Come closer.

11
00:08:41,958 --> 00:08:43,833
Total value, 3 million dollars.

12
00:08:44,375 --> 00:08:45,666
What about the ones in the briefcase?

13
00:08:46,041 --> 00:08:47,333
They're fake.

14
00:08:49,541 --> 00:08:51,666
You need to tie this to your leg.

15
00:08:53,916 --> 00:08:55,958
And don't tell your cousin.

16
00:09:12,875 --> 00:09:13,791
Walk.

17
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:15,625
Yeah it's fine.

18
00:09:19,916 --> 00:09:21,750
See that car across the street?

19
00:09:22,291 --> 00:09:24,708
He's gonna follow you to Houghtons.